{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_04_02",
  "title": "神崎莉央",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……\nまだまだ、この程度じゃ足りないわ……",
      "startTime": 2.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（今日のダンスレッスン、莉央さんはいつも以上に）\n（気合いが入ってるな……）",
      "startTime": 10.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、いつにも増して練習に熱が入ってますけど\n何かあったんですか？",
      "startTime": 15.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "来週、映画のプロモーション用の写真を\n撮影することになったでしょ？",
      "startTime": 20.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "だから万全の状態で撮影に臨むために\nダンスの練習量を増やすことにしたのよ",
      "startTime": 26.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "写真を撮るのに\nどうしてダンスの練習を増やす必要があるんですか？",
      "startTime": 30.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "それは、アクション映画にふさわしい肉体を作るためよ",
      "startTime": 34.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "撮影では、私を映画のヒロインに見立てて\n写真を撮ることになるわ",
      "startTime": 42.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "つまり、私はケイティの代理なの",
      "startTime": 44.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "ケイティは過酷な肉体改造をして映画に取り組んだ……\nだったら私も相応の体作りをしないと……",
      "startTime": 52.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そこまでしなくても\n莉央さんは今のままで十分格好いいと思いますけど……",
      "startTime": 58.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "分かっていないようね\n私はハリウッドスターのケイティと比較されるのよ",
      "startTime": 64.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "生半可な覚悟じゃ恥をかくのは目に見えてるわ\n半端な気持ちで彼女の代理は務まらないのよ",
      "startTime": 72.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "話題性だけでアイドルを起用したなんて言わせない\n私がやるからには全力でヒロインを表現してみせる！",
      "startTime": 79.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "意気込みは分かりますけど、体を鍛えるなら\nもっと効率のいいやり方があるんじゃないですか？",
      "startTime": 86.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "「効率的なやり方なんてつまらないでしょ」\n……今のは映画の中でケイティが言ったセリフよ",
      "startTime": 93.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "仲間から「もっと要領よく出来たんじゃないか」って\n問われてそう答えたの。クールな返しだと思わない？",
      "startTime": 100.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "クールかどうかは別にして、莉央さんが\nケイティの映画が好きだという想いは伝わりました",
      "startTime": 108.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "そうよ、私はケイティの映画が好きなの。大ファンなの\nだから妥協したくないのよ！",
      "startTime": 117.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "わ、分かりました。でもハードワークには気をつけて\nくれぐれも無理だけはしないで下さい",
      "startTime": 123.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 127.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-02-000-noon",
      "startTime": 128.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（莉央さん、少し痩せてきたんじゃないか？）\n（それに動きに精彩がない……）",
      "startTime": 133.5,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6633.333333299987,
          "startTime": 140.1333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……",
      "startTime": 137.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です\n途中、ふらついてましたけど体調が悪いんですか？",
      "startTime": 143.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "……うまくフォローしたつもりだったけど\nそういうところはしっかり見てるのね",
      "startTime": 150,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "心配しないで、体調は問題ないわ\nちょっと打ち身で体が痛むだけだから",
      "startTime": 156.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "打ち身って……怪我をしたんですか！？\n一体何があったんです？",
      "startTime": 163.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "アクション映画の格好良さを表現するために\n最近、殺陣を教わっているのよ",
      "startTime": 168.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "殺陣は知ってるでしょ？　映画やドラマで\n格闘シーンを格好良く見せる芝居のことよ",
      "startTime": 174.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんがやるのは写真撮影ですよ？\n実際にアクションをする訳じゃないのに……",
      "startTime": 181.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "だとしても、アクションの見せ方を知っていた方が\nより迫力や臨場感を出せるはずよ",
      "startTime": 188.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "でもダンスだけでも大変なのに殺陣の練習まで……\n体を絞るために食事制限もしてるそうじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 195.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "最近の莉央さんは糖分が足りてないから\nカリカリしていて怖いってこころが言ってましたよ",
      "startTime": 202.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "こころがそんなことを……\nあの子とは後でじっくり話す必要がありそうね",
      "startTime": 208.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "（しまった、藪蛇だったか。すまん、こころ……）",
      "startTime": 212.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-rio021.m4a",
      "text": "確かに大変だけど、ケイティが演じるヒロインを\n完璧に再現するために全て必要なことよ",
      "startTime": 220.6333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "完璧に再現するって……\n先方も莉央さんにそこまで求めていないと思いますよ",
      "startTime": 227.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_02-rio022.m4a",
      "text": "映画の中でケイティは「お前がトレジャーハンターか」\nと問われて、クールにこう答えているわ",
      "startTime": 234.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
